headline: Agoda Reveals Top Family-Friendly Local Getaways This Summer Break
summary: With the school summer break fast approaching, Filipino families are gearing up for their much-anticipated vacations. During this summer holiday period, Filipino families showcased a 39% higher preference for domestic over international travel, according to Agoda accommodation search data.
